53
0:02:38.497,000 --> 0:02:39,000
And hemoglobin acts as a molecular sponge

54
0:02:40.488,000 --> 0:02:41,000
to soak up the oxygen in your lungs

55
0:02:42.189,000 --> 0:02:44,000
and then carry it to other parts of the body.

56
0:02:44.326,000 --> 0:02:46,000
I was very much inspired by this image many years ago,

57
0:02:46.882,000 --> 0:02:48,000
