146
0:06:26.57,000 --> 0:06:29,000
So this is one of the biggest molecular structures that you have,

147
0:06:29.656,000 --> 0:06:32,000
at least as far as we've discovered so far inside of us.

148
0:06:33.286,000 --> 0:06:34,000
